NAME
    libchimera - utility shared library for HAMcast modules

BUILD/INSTALL

Requirements
    - cmake (Version 2.6+)
    - openssl libraries developers edition
    - pthread library

Build
    We recommend an 'out-of-source' cmake-build. Create a new folder, e.g.
    'build' within the source directory. Change to new folder (cd build)
    and run:

        cmake ../

    This will initialize build environment, if no errors occure run:

        make

    afterwards. If build was successful you find the library in build folder.

Install
    Not supported

SYNOPSIS
    None.

DESCRIPTION
    libchimera provides an pastry based P2P overlay network to be used by
    certain HAMcast modules such as Scribe and BIDIR-SAM.

EXIT STATUS
    None.

OPTIONS
    None.

EXAMPLES
    None.

FILES
    No other files required or used.

ENVIRONMENT
    NONE.

NOTES
    None.

